title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Clearing up murky goals can lead to concrete results. Sometimes, its tough to acknowledge that pipe dreams are off-key, but thats exactly what you might have to acknowledge today. Bombastic Jupiter grinds into a square with lofty Neptune, prompting you to overreach for an objective. You may be unrealistic about your ambitions or the skills of those youre working with now. However, tapping into your creative wellsprings empowers you to make the necessary corrections to keep on track or even soar ahead. Taking your inspiration to the next level is music to your ears.
